title: Trainsignal Systems Security Certified Practitioner SSCP Trainin
description:
FORMAT: ISO
RUNTIME: 19H 57M
RELEASE DATE: 2013/08/14
STORE DATE: 2013/06/28
AUTHOR: TONY NORTHRUP - DISKS: 16 x 50MB

This course will prepare you for the Systems Security Certified Practitioner
(SSCPr) certification. Learn about cool topics like access controls, security
operations, security administration, monitoring, analysis, risks, responses
recovery, cryptography, networks, communication, malicious code, and malicious
activity. This training course is the perfect entry-level course for someone
looking to launch their career in security or advance their current security
position
